# Company: Stackpak

- Website: https://stackpak.dev
- Founder(s): George Fahmy
- Location: US
- Primary Category: Cloud Infrastructure

## What they do
Stackpak helps teams manage and optimize cloud infrastructure with visibility tools.

## Target user (ICP)
DevOps and cloud infrastructure teams.

## Key features
- Infra visibility
- Optimization insights
- Cost tracking

## Pricing
Usage-based

## Positioning
“Understand your cloud stack.”

## Overlap with Clode
- Cloud infrastructure management

## How Clode is different
- Clode automates actions, not just insights

## DevRel angle
Visibility without automation still creates work.

